Class SetParameterTag

java.lang.Object

      com.tonbeller.jpivot.param.SetParameterTag
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.IterationTag, javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.JspTag, javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.Tag
public class SetParameterTag
extends javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.TagSupport

looks for a http parameter with a certain name. If the parameter is present, the parameter is parsed and set into the MDX Query.

If a sessionParam is specified, its value is set into the MDX query.

av
